#: .\robot_workbench\furniture-surfaces.json .\robot_workbench\items.json
msgid "Stationary CraftBuddy"
msgid_plural "Stationary CraftBuddys"
msgstr[0] "固定式工藝夥伴"

#. ~ Description for Stationary CraftBuddy
#: .\robot_workbench\furniture-surfaces.json
msgid ""
"A robot crafting assistant. Useable as stationary all-purpose craft station "
"and as workbench with great boost to work speed, also help you butcher "
"things near it. Unfolding it into stationary form produced some little "
"AutoPack section you can use to create some auto-crafting packets with "
"simple tasks. Can be dismantled retain it's portable form and functionality."
msgstr ""
"一個機器人制作助手。可用作固定的多功能製作站和工作臺，大幅提升工作速度，還能幫助你處理附近的物品。展開為固定形態時，會產生一個小型自動包部分，可用於創建帶有簡單任務的自動製作包。可拆卸以保留其便攜形態和功能。"

#: .\robot_workbench\furniture-surfaces.json
msgid "metal screeching!"
msgstr "金屬尖嘯聲！"

#: .\robot_workbench\furniture-surfaces.json
msgid "clang!"
msgstr "哐當！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Stationary CraftBuddy'}
#: .\robot_workbench\items.json
msgid ""
"This is a crafting_pseudo_item for craftbuddy bot functions and if you have "
"it as an separate item, something is wrong, WATCH OUT."
msgstr "這是用於工藝夥伴機器人功能的製作偽物品，如果你將其作為獨立物品擁有，說明出了問題，請注意。"

#: .\robot_workbench\tailoring.json
msgid "AutoPack: mending rope to thread"
msgid_plural "AutoPack: mending rope to threads"
msgstr[0] "自動包：將繩索修補成線"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'AutoPack: mending rope to thread'}.
#: .\robot_workbench\tailoring.json
msgid "AutoPack has finished it's production process."
msgstr "自動包已完成其生產過程。"

#. ~ Use action not_ready_msg for {'str': 'AutoPack: mending rope to thread'}.
#: .\robot_workbench\tailoring.json
msgid "AutoPack didn't finished the task yet."
msgstr "自動包尚未完成任務。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'AutoPack: mending rope to thread'}
#: .\robot_workbench\tailoring.json
msgid ""
"Packed automatic assembler that slowly but steadily produce many threads "
"from single rope. Requires assembled and installed stationary CraftBuddy "
"station nearby and some UPS to be packed. Activate it when it's done."
msgstr "打包的自動組裝器，能緩慢但穩定地從單根繩索生產大量線。需要附近有組裝並安裝好的固定式工藝夥伴站和一些UPS電源才能打包。完成後激活它。"

#: .\robot_workbench\tailoring.json
msgid "AutoPack with threads from a single long rope"
msgid_plural "AutoPack with threads from a single long ropes"
msgstr[0] "自動包：從單根長繩索生產線"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'AutoPack with threads from a single long rope'}
#: .\robot_workbench\tailoring.json
msgid ""
"A inactive AutoPack that finished it's work and disassembled single long "
"rope into large units of thread."
msgstr "一個已停用的自動包，完成了工作並將單根長繩索分解為大量線單位。"
